### Seed
  GET http://localhost:8080/api/seed

### PostgreSQL - all products
  GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

### PostgreSQL - by category
  GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/category/ELECTRONICS

### MongoDB - all products
  GET http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/products

### MongoDB - by tag
  GET http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/products/tag/apple

### MongoDB - category averages
  GET http://localhost:8080/api/mongo/products/analytics/category-avg

### Cassandra - sensor readings
  GET http://localhost:8080/api/sensors/user-activity-alice/readings/latest?limit=5

### Neo4j - recommendations
  GET http://localhost:8080/api/graph/persons/Alice/recommendations?limit=5

### Neo4j - friends of friends
  GET http://localhost:8080/api/graph/persons/Alice/fof

### Elasticsearch - full text search
  GET http://localhost:8080/api/search?q=laptop

### Elasticsearch - by name
  GET http://localhost:8080/api/search/products/name?q=macbook

### Smart page (all 6 DBs)
  GET http://localhost:8080/api/smart/product/1?userName=Alice

### ── Purchase Flow ─────────────────────────────────────

### POST purchase
POST http://localhost:8080/55-22068/purchases
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "personName": "Alice",
  "productId": 46,
  "quantity": 2,
  "purchaseDetails": {
    "paymentMethod": "VISA ending 4242",
    "shippingAddress": "123 Main St, Cairo",
    "giftWrap": true,
    "couponCode": "SAVE10"
  }
}

### Verify PostgreSQL stock deducted
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/46

### Verify MongoDB receipt
GET http://localhost:8080/55-22068/purchases/person/Alice

### Verify Neo4j recommendations (Bob follows Alice)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/graph/persons/Bob/recommendations?limit=5

### Verify Cassandra activity log
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sensors/user-activity-alice/readings

### Verify Elasticsearch
GET http://localhost:8080/api/search/products/category/ELECTRONICS